rence<\/li>\n<li>Fraud in the inducement\/execution<\/li>\n<li>Conversion<\/li>\n<li>Trespass to Chattels<\/li>\n<li>Fraudulent concealment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Addressing &amp; Taking Legal Action Against Business Fraud<\/h2>\n<p>We recognize that the best way to address business fraud is to do so swiftly and diligently.<\/p>\n<p>Our team of experienced lawyers urges anyone who may be the victim of fraud to seek counsel as quickly as possible to minimize the immediate impact and mitigate the chance of future problems.<\/p>\n<p>To assist you in this process, we offer access to our team via phone and email at both the  Fresno and Fresno offices. Your concerns will be promptly addressed so that you can take the next step, whatever that may be.<\/p>\n<h2>True GRIT to Handle Your Most Difficult Legal Matters<\/h2>\n<p>Business Fraud has widespread implications, and therefore it\u2019s imperative that you work with one of the best mortgage, investment, and business fraud attorneys in the  Fresno and Fresnno County.<\/p>\n<p>Our aggressive trial lawyers have exactly what it takes to bring the perpetrators to court and find justice for you and all who are impacted. The best way to describe us is by having true GRIT: Goal Oriented, Resilient, Intuitive, and Trustworthy.<\/p>\n<h2>Free Initial Evaluation<\/h2>\n<p>Each and every client deserves access to lawyers that will be aggressive in the courtroom while showing you, the client, nothing but honest and compassionate professionalism.<\/p>\n<p>To help clients begin the legal process, we offer each potential new client a free initial case evaluation.\u00a0 Should you choose to contact us, we can help you determine your rights, evaluate your interests, and discuss potential remedies.<\/p>\n<p>Find out how we can help you by calling our  Fresno office at 415-217-9456 or our Fresno office at 415-217-9456. Or, sign up for a <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\